ass=\"bb_paragraph\" >About 2 hours. If you are experienced it might be closer to 1:45, and if you take your time it's closer to 3.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480990/extras/ccc31133e7d5e1981c443fa1e366a9ad.poster.avif?t=1768344478\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480990/extras/ccc31133e7d5e1981c443fa1e366a9ad.webm?t=1768344478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480990/extras/ccc31133e7d5e1981c443fa1e366a9ad.mp4?t=1768344478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
